1 0 0 1 50 592 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 578 Tm (y = W x + b) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 564 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 550 Tm (Meaning:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 536 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 522 Tm (- x = input vector) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm (- W = learned weight matrix) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm (- b = learned bias) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (- y = transformed vector) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm () Tj
