1 0 0 1 50 438 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 424 Tm ("transparent turquoise glass warrior") Tj
1 0 0 1 50 410 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 396 Tm (into dense numerical meaning vectors.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 382 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 368 Tm (weight_dtype affects how accurately W, x, b, and y are represented.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 354 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 340 Tm (2. Attention Decides What Matters) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 326 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 312 Tm (Attention is how the model lets different parts of the prompt and image latent influence) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 298 Tm ( each other.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 284 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 270 Tm (attention = softmax\(Q K^T / sqrt\(d\)\) V) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 256 Tm () Tj
