1 0 0 1 50 760 Tm (learned visual and language knowledge.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 746 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 732 Tm (Attention uses those transformed vectors. Q, K, and V are usually created by learned ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 718 Tm (linear projections:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 704 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 690 Tm (Q = Wq x + bq) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 676 Tm (K = Wk context + bk) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 662 Tm (V = Wv context + bv) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 648 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 634 Tm (So y = W x + b is not separate from attention. It is inside attention. The model first ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 620 Tm (uses learned matrices to create Q, K, and V. Then attention compares Q and K, and mixes ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 606 Tm (V.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 592 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 578 Tm (For cross-attention inside the UNet:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 564 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 550 Tm (- x is often the current noisy image latent features.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 536 Tm (- context is often the text embeddings from the prompt.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 522 Tm (- Q comes from the current image latent.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm (- K and V come from the prompt/text embeddings.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (That means the noisy image asks, through Q: "What prompt information is relevant to this) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm ( visual region right now?") Tj
1 0 0 1 50 452 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 438 Tm (The prompt answers, through K and V: "Here are concepts like glass, warrior, turquoise, ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 424 Tm (running, and isometric view.") Tj
1 0 0 1 50 410 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 396 Tm (Then:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 382 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 368 Tm (softmax\(Q K^T / sqrt\(d\)\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 354 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 340 Tm (computes how strongly each visual position should attend to each prompt concept. ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 326 Tm (Multiplying by V injects the relevant prompt information back into the image features.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 312 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 298 Tm (So the two equations interact like this:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 284 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 270 Tm (1. Linear layers create features and Q/K/V:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 256 Tm (   Q = Wq latent + bq) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 242 Tm (   K = Wk text + bk) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 228 Tm (   V = Wv text + bv) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 214 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 200 Tm (2. Attention matches image features to text concepts:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 186 Tm (   attention = softmax\(Q K^T / sqrt\(d\)\) V) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 172 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 158 Tm (3. More linear layers transform the attention output:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 144 Tm (   y = W attention + b) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 130 Tm () Tj
ET
endstream
