1 0 0 1 50 746 Tm (   noise_prediction = UNet\(latent, text_embeddings, timestep\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 732 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 718 Tm (Expanded Explanation: How Scheduler And VAE Interact) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 704 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 690 Tm (The scheduler and VAE operate at different parts of the pipeline.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 676 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 662 Tm (The scheduler works in latent space. It does not create RGB pixels. It updates the ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 648 Tm (compressed latent representation step by step.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 634 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 620 Tm (At each denoising step:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 606 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 592 Tm (noise_prediction = UNet\(latent_t, text_embeddings, timestep_t\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 578 Tm (latent_t_minus_1 = scheduler_step\(latent_t, noise_prediction, timestep_t\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 564 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 550 Tm (The scheduler asks: given the current latent and the noise predicted by the UNet, what ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 536 Tm (should the next cleaner latent be?) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 522 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 508 Tm (After the final denoising step, you have:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 494 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 480 Tm (final_latent) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 466 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 452 Tm (This final_latent is not directly viewable as an image. It is a compact tensor ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 438 Tm (representation. The VAE decoder then maps it into pixel space:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 424 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 410 Tm (image = VAE_decode\(final_latent\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 396 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 382 Tm (So the scheduler and VAE interact sequentially:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 368 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 354 Tm (1. Scheduler repeatedly refines the latent.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 340 Tm (2. VAE decodes only the final refined latent into RGB pixels.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 326 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 312 Tm (The VAE does not usually participate in every denoising step for text-to-image. It is ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 298 Tm (mostly used at the end to decode the final latent. For image editing, the VAE may also ) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 284 Tm (be used at the beginning to encode the input image into latent space.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 270 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 256 Tm (Precise simplified chain:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 242 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 228 Tm (input prompt -> text embeddings) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 214 Tm (seed -> latent_T) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 200 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 186 Tm (for each timestep t:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 172 Tm (    noise_prediction_t = UNet\(latent_t, text_embeddings, t\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 158 Tm (    latent_t_minus_1 = scheduler_step\(latent_t, noise_prediction_t, t\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 144 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 130 Tm (final_latent = latent_0) Tj
